    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\t\t\t     Love Song - Tesla\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nTabbed By: O. Briseno\r\ne-mail: omar.bs@gmail.com\r\n\r\nTuning: EADG (Standard)\r\n\r\nNo bass in the intro\r\n\r\n[tab]So you think...\r\nG|----------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------9-----------------------------|\r\nA|----------------2------2/7-----7-----------2--------------|\r\nE|---7\\0----------------------------0---------------5-------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Any time you...                                  ...if you need a friend\r\nG|------------------7-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|---5/7-------7/9----9--5----------5--7\\---------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------------------2---5-----|\r\nE|------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]It's gonna take a little time...\r\nG|------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------9-------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------2------2/7-----7-----------2----------------|\r\nE|---7\\0----------------------------0---------------5---------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Don't you even worry...\r\nG|------------------7-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|---5/7-------7/9----9--5----------5--7\\---------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------------------2---5-----|\r\nE|------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]BRIDGE\r\nG|----------------------|\r\nD|----------------------|\r\nA|----5--5--5-----------|\r\nE|---------------7\\3----|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Love is all around...\r\nG|------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------5---4------------------5---4/7---------------------| \r\nA|----------------------5---------------------5---------------| \r\nE|---3--3------------------3--3-------------------------------| x2[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Waiting for you...\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------7-------3----3-3-3-------5---------5---5-----5-----|\r\nE|--0------0-----------------------------------5---5-----5---5--3|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]SOLO (x2)\r\nG|------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-----------------2---2-2------2---2----------------2--------|\r\nE|--0-----0--0-5--------------2---2---2-0-----0--0------5-----|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------7-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|---5/7-------7/9----9--5-----5-7\\---------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------2--2--2--2-----5------|\r\nE|---------------------------------------------------5--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Love will find a way...\r\nG|------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------5-------5---5------------3/15\\----------------|\r\nE|--3--3--3--3--------5---5----0-----0------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------5-------5---5---7--7--7--5-----3--------------|\r\nE|--3--3--3--3--------5---5-----------------------------------| x3[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| \\  slide down\r\n| h  hammer-on\r\n| p  pull-off\r\n| ~  vibrato\r\n| +  harmonic\r\n| x  Mute note\r\n===============================================================================",
